README file for plagg

$Id$


Installation
------------

0. Install Mark Pilgrim's Ultra-liberal Feed Parser 3.3 from
   http://feedparser.org/
1. Untar the distribution file to a directory of your choice
2. Move the blagg script to a directory in your $PATH
3. Adjust the path in the call to sys.path.insert to the
   path you have chosen in step 1
4. Adjust the names of your OPML file and your news directory.
5. Run plagg each hour from a cron job.
